179:   - `MORE_AVAILABLE` - The SourceReader has more records available immediately.
180:   - `NOTHING_AVAILABLE` - The SourceReader does not have more records available at this point, but may have more records in the future.
181:   - `END_OF_INPUT` - The SourceReader has exhausted all the records and reached the end of data. This means the SourceReader can be closed.
